# Development Workflow

## Setup and Running
- Install dependencies with `npm install`
- Run development server with `npm run dev`
- Build for production with `npm run build`
- Start production server with `npm run start`

## Quality Checks
- Run linting with `npm run lint`
- Run TypeScript checks with `npm run typecheck`
- Run tests with `npm run test`
- Run all checks with `npm run check-all`

## Git Workflow
- The project uses conventional commits
- Git hooks are set up with Husky for:
  - Pre-commit linting and testing
  - Commit message validation
- See [GIT_HOOKS.md](mdc:GIT_HOOKS.md) for more details

## Database
- Seeding and migration scripts are available in [scripts](mdc:scripts) directory
